### Why This Format is Necessary for the Project

1. **It acts as a Manifest for AI Context Windows:** By keeping this map at the top of the repository, you can feed it to AI assistant tools to instantly constrain their code-generation outputs to the strict hierarchy of the project.
2. **It Explicitly Bridges the "Two Realities":** It shows developers exactly why Pattern 4 (`step`) or Pattern 7 can exist as an example file right now without crashing the production prototype build, thanks to Section 4's feature-gate reference map.
3. **It Anchors Your Negative Test Strategy:** When building the Phase 7 negative test suite, your test harness can use this document's file maps to automatically assert that cross-document validation rules are fully satisfied before tagging a release as secure.